@author "William Eaves"
@$VER: 3DStars Guide 1.0 (08.03.09)
@remark Created with golded 8.10 (15.9.7)
@index INDEX
@node MAIN "3D Stars Keys"
  If you are using a non-English keyboard layout, press the keys in same
  location as their English counterparts.  The longer you hold down a
  motion key the more the effect is applied.

       Key set 1         Function                      Key set 2
    ==============================================================

  (on standard keyboard)                           (on numeric keypad)


           ,              Rotate down                       2
           i              Rotate up                         8
           j              Rotate left                       4
           l              Rotate right                      6
           o              Rotate clockwise                  9
           u              Rotate counterclockwise           7
         CSR Up           Move forward
        CSR Down          Move backward
           k              Stop                              5
           x              Move Viewpoint back               0
           c              Move Viewpoint forward            .
           q              Jump to the Sun                   *
           = (+)          Increase brightness               +
           -              Decrease brightness               -
           w              Zoom out                          1
           e              Zoom in                           3
           h              Come to a gradual stop

           s              Turn stereo view on/off         Enter
           r              Increase stereo screen plane position
           t              Decrease stereo screen plane position
           f              Increase stereo effect
           g              Decrease stereo effect

           p		  Toggles between Pause/Running

          ESC             Quit


  MENU SHORTCUTS
  ==============

  CMD Q			  Quit
  CMD *			  Reset Stars
  CMD S                   Toggle Statistics Display
  CMD T                   Toggle Screen Title Bar


@endnode
